00:33:09.594 --> 00:33:10.719
DAYAMRITA CHAITANYA: Right.

00:33:14.240 --> 00:33:14.980
AUDIENCE: Hello.

00:33:14.980 --> 00:33:19.030
I'm Igor and I have a
